    },
    {
      "kind": 2,
      "value": "(3.34858341214434152511372813064699522256050903805500162810692667634701\\\n35908877050562598120454508271117870686627559178`99.99999384998786)/(3.54067843175984697176921476083682275484055790079634978293051489296322\\\n29045575339036297151150375743916320798959498156`99.99999674040212)",
      "languageId": "wolfram"
    },
    {
      "kind": 2,
      "value": "SimpleTest[L_]:=Module[{storedMat,storedMat1,storedMat2,storedMat3,storedMat4, storedMat5,det1,det2,det3,det4,det5},\nstoredMat=DirectMatN[L,prec];\nstoredMat1=DirectRedTracedMat[L,L/10,L/10,storedMat];\nstoredMat2=DirectRedTracedMat[L,L/10,L/5,storedMat];\nstoredMat3=DirectRedTracedMat[L,L/4-1,L/4-1,storedMat];\nstoredMat4=DirectRedTracedMat[L,L/4,L/4,storedMat];\nstoredMat5=DirectRedTracedMat[L,L/6,L/6,storedMat];\ndet1=Det[storedMat1]/(L/2);\ndet2=Det[storedMat2]/(L/2);\ndet3=Det[storedMat3]/(L/2);\ndet4=Det[storedMat4]/(L/2);\ndet5=Det[storedMat5]/(L/2);\nPrint[{L,det1/det2}];\nReturn[{L,det1,det2,det3,det4,det5},Module];\n]",
      "languageId": "wolfram"
    },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "value": "\\<\\\nThe output of the following is a table of\n{L, DetPrime[L, L/10, L/10], DetPrime[L, L/10, L/5], DetPrime[L, L/4-1, \\\nL/4-1], DetPrime[L, L/4, L/4], DetPrime[L, L/6, L/6]}\nThe Printed lines (not output) are {L, DetPrime[L, L/10, L/10] / DetPrime[L, \\\nL/10, L/5]}\\\n\\>",
      "languageId": "markdown"
    },
